  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relive the nostalgia of your school desk in this golf game for Steam!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Play]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategize to conquer your favorite courses with a variety of settings!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with 9 or 18 holes and compete for high scores on the online leaderboards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Friendly Match]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with up to 4 people!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in serious showdowns with stroke play or match play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Edit]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely arrange and design your own original course!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a unique 18-hole course all your own!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Gacha]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your points to obtain new clubs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your ultimate favorite!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Minigame]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hit the ball and aim for big points!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn points based on where the ball lands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>To receive news and update notifications</strong><br>Please click on <strong>Developer: SAT-BOX</strong> at the top of the store page and <strong>Follow</strong> us!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Relive the nostalgia of your school desk in this golf game for Steam!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Play]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strategize to conquer your favorite courses with a variety of settings!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with 9 or 18 holes and compete for high scores on the online leaderboards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Friendly Match]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with up to 4 people!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in serious showdowns with stroke play or match play!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Edit]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Freely arrange and design your own original course!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a unique 18-hole course all your own!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Gacha]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your points to obtain new clubs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find your ultimate favorite!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Minigame]</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hit the ball and aim for big points!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn points based on where the ball lands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>To receive news and update notifications</strong><br>Please click on <strong>Developer: SAT-BOX</strong> at the top of the store page and <strong>Follow</strong> us!</p>",
